    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ee Wahrdi Jeremijus/ ta Dehla Jiktius/ weena no teem Preeſtercem/ kas Unatotā bija eekſch Benjamina Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Uſ ko ta KUNGA Wahrdē notikte eekſch tahm Deenahm Joſijus/ ta Dehla Amora/ ta Rehnina Juha/ treschapa definitive Gaddā winna Waldischanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tas us winnu notikte eekſch tahm Deenahm Jojakima/ ta Dehla Josijus/ ta Rehnina Juha/ famehr pabeigts tappe tas weenpadeſinitais Gads Jedekijus/ ta Dehla Josijus/ ta Rehnina Juha/ ka Jerusalemes (Laudis) tappe nisweſti peektā Mehneti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta KUNGA Wahrdē notikte uhs manni/ kas tazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pirms es tewi Mahtes Meeſā padarriju/ eſmu es tewi paſinnis/ un pirns tu no Mah tes Meeſahm isnahzi/ eſmu es etvi ſwehtijis/ es eſmu tewi eein Laudim par weenu Pra veetu lizzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazziju es: Ak KUNGS KUNGS! raugi/esne peeman nu runnaht/ jo es eſmu jauns.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas KUNGS fazzija us manni: Ne faſſt/ es eſmu jauns/ jo wiſtur/ kurp es tewt fuhttischu/ buhs tew ect/ un wiſfu/ ko es tew pawehleschu/ buhs tew runnaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne bihſtees preekſch winreem/ jo es eſmu ar tewim/ un iſglahbschu tewi/ faſka tas KUNGS:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS iſteepe fatwu Rohku/ un aiſkahre mannu Mutti/ un tas KUNGS fazzija us manni: Raugi/es lee eu mannu Wahrdutawa Mutte.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Reds/ es eezettu tewi ſchodeen pahr teem Laudim/ un pahr tahm Walſtibahm/ iſraut un falaufibt/ un famaitaht/ un iſpohſtiht/ ir ustaiſiht un dehſiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wehl notikte ta KUNGA Wahrdē uhs manni/ un fazzija: Ko redſi tu Jeremijus? Un es fazziju: Es redsu weenu Mandeka-Rihksti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija us manni: Tu eſt labbi redsejs/ jo es buhſchu mohdrigs * pahr tawu Wahrdū/ ka es to darru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta KUNGA Wahrdē notikte uhs manni ohtra Reise/ un fazzija: Ko redſi tu? Un es\n"
    }
  ],
